            <fr:title text="Relational extensionality">Relational extensionality</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> be two sets, and let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R,S\colon  A\mathbin {\nrightarrow } B]]></fr:tex> be two <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00I7.xml" title="Relation" addr="jms-00I7" type="local">relations</fr:link> from <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex>. Then we have <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R=S]]></fr:tex> if and only if <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\forall {a\in  A}\mathpunct {.} \forall {b\in  B}\mathpunct {.} a\mathrel {R}b\Longleftrightarrow  a\mathrel {S}b]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
 
   
